## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of how perception influences communication. The subjective nature of perception means that its effects can vary widely among individuals and contexts, which may not be fully captured in this report. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources limits the ability to verify the accuracy of all claims made in the cited articles. Further empirical research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.